| Column              | Description                       |
| ------------------- | --------------------------------- |
| `price`             | Selling price of the car          |
| `age_08_04`         | Age in months as of August 2004   |
| `mfg_year`          | Year of manufacturing             |
| `km`                | Kilometers driven (mileage)       |
| `fuel_type`         | Fuel type (Petrol, Diesel, etc.)  |
| `hp`                | Horsepower                        |
| `met_color`         | 1 if metallic color, 0 otherwise  |
| `color`             | Color of the car                  |
| `automatic`         | 1 = Automatic transmission        |
| `cc`                | Engine displacement in cc         |
| `doors`             | Number of doors                   |
| `gears`             | Transmission gears                |
| `quarterly_tax`     | Estimated quarterly road tax      |
| `weight`            | Weight of the car (kg)            |
| `mfr_guarantee`     | 1 = Manufacturer guarantee valid  |
| `bovag_guarantee`   | 1 = BOVAG guarantee valid         |
| `abs`               | Anti-lock Braking System          |
| `airbag_1`          | Driver airbag                     |
| `airbag_2`          | Passenger airbag                  |
| `airco`             | Air conditioning                  |
| `automatic_airco`   | Automatic air conditioning system |
| `boardcomputer`     | Onboard computer                  |
| `cd_player`         | CD player installed               |
| `central_lock`      | Central locking system            |
| `powered_windows`   | Power windows                     |
| `power_steering`    | Power steering system             |
| `mistlamps`         | Fog lights                        |
| `parking_assistant` | Parking sensors                   |
| `tow_bar`           | Tow bar installed                 |
